{"tid":2383854,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲礦商股票因代碼與Gme太像 股價一度漲53％","createTime":"2021-01-28T07:38:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T08:30:21.000Z","uid":28765,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4dac4ada6bf37c74bdbe80943c2b25b5bfc1c64f","tid":2383854,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T07:38:52.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕美國遊戲零售商GameStop股價持續瘋漲，而澳洲小型礦商的股票代碼因與GameStop的代碼都有GME，這才讓部分投資人搞錯，促使這家礦商的股價在週四一度大暴漲53％，連公司董事都傻眼。<br />\n<br />\n據《路透》報導，澳洲小型鎳鈷礦商GME Resources股價週四一度飆漲53％，收盤上漲13％，至8.5澳分，當日漲幅為1澳分；週三則上漲了14％。GME Resources的股價會飆漲主要是因為其股票代碼，和GameStop太相似。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\nGME Resources的發言人未對此發表評論。然而，GME Resources的常務董事沙利文（Peter Sullivan）表示，這一激增令他感到驚訝，他形容當他看到股價是9.4美分時，很震驚、整個爆炸了，他說他還想：「嗯，這是怎麼回事？我自己的公司有什麼我不知道的東西嗎？」後來他才知道，是因為他們的股票代碼與GME有關。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3425119\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3425119&d=LvSu6Mc%2FVB7R449T953cU0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=4c235d2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3425119&h=7865aa2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3425119</a>"},{"pid":"9a1e688dc0bf884142a7019c29fcc88afc2981c8","tid":2383854,"uid":9116,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T07:39:46.000Z","msg":"成日都炒錯同名系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ef4b542a946d0c460846c627307f9eb76ec2b5","tid":2383854,"uid":69899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T07:41:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e74416b5cc6d44d33e853a7b9052e4843d731558","tid":2383854,"uid":208376,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTim